valid = []
valid.append('1-1,1-2,1-3,1-4,1-5')
valid.append('2-1,2-2,2-3,2-4,2-5')
valid.append('3-1,3-2,3-3,3-4,3-5')
valid.append('4-1,4-2,4-3,4-4,4-5')
valid.append('5-1,5-2,5-3,5-4,5-5')
actual = self.runner('-r 1:-1', None, '-c 1:-1', None, options=
    "--delimiter=',' --quoting=quote_none")
assert valid == actual
actual = self.runner(None, '-R 0,-1', None, '-C 0,-1', options=
    "--delimiter=',' --quoting=quote_none")
assert valid == actual
